  "title": "🗣️Client Relationship Executive (1-to1-mentorship)",
  "description": "<p>🚀 <strong>Your Career, Your Rules — Get Paid to Level Up!</strong><br />No experience? No worries. Represent top brands, <strong>earn as you learn</strong>, and <strong>travel the world</strong> 🌍💰</p><h3>🔥 What You’ll Do</h3><p>• Represent brands at events, roadshows & campaigns<br />• Engage customers & strengthen communication skills<br />• Support sales & marketing campaigns<br />• Learn from leaders & grow into leadership roles</p><h3>👀 Who You Are</h3><p>• Fresh graduates, ORD personnel, or career switchers<br />• Confident (or willing to learn) communicators<br />• Positive, motivated, and hungry to grow professionally<br /></p><h3>✨ Why You’ll Love It</h3><p>💰 Weekly pay + uncapped incentives<br />🧑‍🏫 1-to-1 mentorship & skill-building workshops<br />✈️🌍 Travel locally & overseas<br />🤩 Fun, high-energy, supportive team culture<br />⚡ Fast career growth & leadership opportunities<br /></p><p>📩 <strong>Apply now — your next career chapter starts here!</strong></p>",
